        <h2>The verdict</h2>
        <p>ConstructionOnline is a solid platform that deserves more attention than it gets. Its estimating capabilities are genuinely strong, and for contractors who need to produce detailed specifications and proposals, it may be a better fit than Buildertrend. The tradeoff is a smaller community, a less polished modern UX, and a smaller integration ecosystem.</p>

        <p>If you're evaluating it alongside Buildertrend, run both demos and compare the estimating modules specifically — that's where UDA genuinely shines.</p>

